## Findings

### 🔴 High — PII exposed without authentication (A01: Broken Access Control / A04: Insecure Design)

`GET /users` returns email addresses to any unauthenticated caller. Even though the data is hard-coded today, the endpoint shape establishes a pattern that is broken by default.

