| SSRF | None — no outbound HTTP | `fetch`/`axios` to user URLs |
| Insecure deserialization | None — default JSON only | `eval`, `vm`, `yaml.load`, custom parsers |
| XSS | N/A — JSON-only responses | any HTML rendering, `res.send(html)` |

